### 2. How to bind invite code

Go to the[ ](https://www.asterdex.com/en/stage1/team)[S2 landing page](https://www.asterdex.com/en/stage2/team) and connect your wallet. Click \[Bind your invite code quickly]. Enter your inviter’s code. Once done, you will see yourself in the Inviter Team.

